{"tid":374150,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"安盛傳裁香港IT部門250員工","createTime":"2017-08-25T14:00:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-26T14:55:48.000Z","uid":84436,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1292202db1a65d605d0296989d90ee10fff2451d","tid":374150,"uid":84436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T14:00:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/hongkong/article/1641507\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fhongkong%2Farticle%2F1641507&d=RlaQ%2Fiq9qU2E4FC%2FJh44NW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=80179019\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/hongkong/article/1641507</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n路透引述兩名知情人士透露，法國保險公司安盛(AXA)正裁減香港資訊科技(IT)部門約250個職位，以配合公司削減成本計劃。<br />\n<br />\n消息人士表示，根據重組計劃，安盛正在馬尼拉及吉隆坡各設立一個資訊科技中心，並計劃為該兩個新中心合共招聘約400人。目前，安盛的亞洲資訊科技業務是由香港管理。<br />\n<br />\n安盛則回應指，已建立一個強大的亞洲技術平台，而目前正致力於改善相關功能，將涉及到重新調整亞洲的一些職位。"},{"pid":"999352e7b7b1962e4e5704fd0dcc0e9394cf77d7","tid":374150,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T14:01:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"36b3e437072b7a6b6140b96eb5462aab9e8e05a8","tid":374150,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T14:01:34.000Z","msg":"又話it好好搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0386003112192cb717d7d13d8bb8388f5c868f48","tid":374150,"uid":32655,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T14:03:22.000Z","msg":"又係IT狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc1b1e8845fb8a1f69af6303b68e1ef1dde23f2f","tid":374150,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T14:04:26.000Z","msg":"condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bdd5be3e46078b053e7a4c05e5670a566836f7a","tid":374150,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T14:04:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdbec710eea74d9087b153a8a3c39bc73c22e74d","tid":374150,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T14:05:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又話it好好搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n蓋老母is a cheater<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b332ff1029e7c1e1aba9fe651267500f3036cfa6","tid":374150,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T14:06:38.000Z","msg":"IT雖受到社會各階層的歡迎，但以IT為生的職業低層員工卻屬於「賤民」，地位在基層市民之下。雖然有些當紅的IT人，能夠擠身豪們，成為達官貴人的座上客，然而在世人的眼中，他們的人格仍然是低下的，因為IT是供人娛樂的「玩意兒」，IT人就是為人取樂的。<br />\n<br />\n看不起IT人並不僅僅是官員，市民也同樣視IT為最下賤的職業。普通人家如有人去做「IT」，都會被認為是有辱家人，是不肖子孫。凡做「IT」的人要被開除族籍，名字不能上族譜，死後不能葬入宗族墳地。因此，很多人從IT之後，隱姓埋名，幾十年不與家人來往，以免玷辱祖宗。"},{"pid":"1357660a11a2762a6c8993cc5dbd7227210f25e7","tid":374150,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T14:09:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/25/220921_dcdb1636b13fa029e046bb3f09ae1157.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F25%2F220921_dcdb1636b13fa029e046bb3f09ae1157.JPG&h=b197fdd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/25/220921_92adb5c808ad6f413cdd36289ace41af.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F25%2F220921_92adb5c808ad6f413cdd36289ace41af.JPG&h=15b8a6e7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1872bc688271493103ec91a903d34a1a56440f93","tid":374150,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T14:10:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/25/221014_ea9a73881e880e806ccfc2592c7a799c.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F25%2F221014_ea9a73881e880e806ccfc2592c7a799c.PNG&h=4e12faac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/25/221014_9b5f454ea3ac9d544bbfb98234399f22.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F25%2F221014_9b5f454ea3ac9d544bbfb98234399f22.PNG&h=1771dd38&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bbbc2f87d9c1217cdbf91ec7d6b9aa3414788460","tid":374150,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T14:10:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f78300e36bfd32e41f921bfb15b30636f078d1a","tid":374150,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T14:11:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Hong Kong No IT</span>"},{"pid":"f576b8f9551620a661fcc6927f253f6809f920db","tid":374150,"uid":84436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T14:11:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20170825/57128347\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20170825%2F57128347&d=RlaQ%2Fiq9qU2E4FC%2FJh44NW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=a898c25a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20170825%2F57128347&h=8b7f33b9\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20170825/57128347</a><br />\n<br />\n又有機構裁減資訊科技（IT）員工！《路透社》引述兩名消息人士報道，保險公司AXA安盛在港裁250人，全部均是IT員工，原因是削減成本，而香港原本是AXA亞洲區的IT總部。<br />\n裁員行動在本周四發生，AXA並同時移師至菲律賓馬尼拉及馬來西亞吉隆坡，在兩處設立資訊科技中心，分別聘請300人及110人，並形容在這些地區設立IT部是「在可負擔的成本上增強部門效能」。<br />\nAXA發言人並無確認或否認裁員一事，僅指出AXA恒常地審視業務，以提升產品種類及服務，並於亞洲建立科技平台，致力提升科技水平及效能，中間或會牽涉部分區域的人手重整。<br />\n資訊科技商會榮譽會長方保僑指出，不少企業因應減省成本，加上香港人工貴，租金貴，故此一些工序由其他地區取代，不過他認為，大企業在裁員前，必須要慎重考慮是否有其他安排，例如內部轉職，否則對其形象並不好。<br />\n今年IT人被企業開刀屬等閒事，例如國泰航空今年5月裁190名經理級以上員工，IT部是重災區，人數多達77人，主要是削減成本考慮。滙豐今年3月有逾百名IT員工收「大信封」，當時發言人回應指，削減成本為該行策略一部份，以確保競爭力及維持運作效率。<br />\nAXA亦於2014年以26億元作價，將香港強積金業務轉售予美國信安，不過當時並未有牽涉裁員。"},{"pid":"8ee0bcecc26365860b433cacd2ff23704a3273b4","tid":374150,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T14:12:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5093c4216cba9eebd3db8619a6d62021d0534ace","tid":374150,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T14:12:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20170825/57128347\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20170825%2F57128347&d=RlaQ%2Fiq9qU2E4FC%2FJh44NW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=a898c25a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20170825%2F57128347&h=8b7f33b9\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20170825/57128347</a><br />\n<br />\n又有機構裁減資訊科技（IT）員工！《路透社》引述兩名消息人士報道，保險公司AXA安盛在港裁250人，全部均是IT員工，原因是削減成本，而香港原本是AXA亞洲區的IT總部。<br />\n裁員行動在本周四發生，AXA並同時移師至菲律賓馬尼拉及馬來西亞吉隆坡，在兩處設立資訊科技中心，分別聘請300人及110人，並形容在這些地區設立IT部是「在可負擔的成本上增強部門效能」。<br />\nAXA發言人並無確認或否認裁員一事，僅指出AXA恒常地審視業務，以提升產品種類及服務，並於亞洲建立科技平台，致力提升科技水平及效能，中間或會牽涉部分區域的人手重整。<br />\n資訊科技商會榮譽會長方保僑指出，不少企業因應減省成本，加上香港人工貴，租金貴，故此一些工序由其他地區取代，不過他認為，大企業在裁員前，必須要慎重考慮是否有其他安排，例如內部轉職，否則對其形象並不好。<br />\n今年IT人被企業開刀屬等閒事，例如國泰航空今年5月裁190名經理級以上員工，IT部是重災區，人數多達77人，主要是削減成本考慮。滙豐今年3月有逾百名IT員工收「大信封」，當時發言人回應指，削減成本為該行策略一部份，以確保競爭力及維持運作效率。<br />\nAXA亦於2014年以26億元作價，將香港強積金業務轉售予美國信安，不過當時並未有牽涉裁員。</blockquote><br />\n唔係不嬲用印度IT咩?"},{"pid":"dca4831ada9b12842b49bdd9ecff202a444ad7c8","tid":374150,"uid":46910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T14:13:36.000Z","msg":"又開it 刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2ea575d4caffa52878e1ac5e7cb2e6ca807f56e","tid":374150,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T14:17:05.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"82ee18e2268bcf9b3199b8cee216b3afb2d7b957","tid":374150,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T14:20:28.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b2ed03bcc59543feea9b0efdd35a32b87b716247","tid":374150,"uid":131915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T14:20:38.000Z","msg":"香港咁唔睇重IT<br />\n呢樣同未來生活指數同生產力有好大關係"},{"pid":"0bff64960dbe392c07177ffb2b818d2606e410f8","tid":374150,"uid":51134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T14:22:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港咁唔睇重IT<br />\n呢樣同未來生活指數同生產力有好大關係</blockquote><br />\n唔明<br />\n你意思係因為it唔可以增加productivity所有香港忽視it？"},{"pid":"684cb37a920c8afcceb2c8b87b28820181219327","tid":374150,"uid":48442,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T14:35:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9c8d067934e6b5244bf212ae382649464d813ca0","tid":374150,"uid":4780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T14:48:38.000Z","msg":"又請埋班垃圾東南亞helpdesk<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c28b52f13e57c8854bdc7c00949b6b1a3bf2628","tid":374150,"uid":52585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T15:06:21.000Z","msg":"有班傻仔又當睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46263c5b8fd4c010d0472d84c19bde2cf1c